fun.connor.lighter.compiler.generator.codegen

Class LocalVariable

  • java.lang.Object
    • fun.connor.lighter.compiler.generator.codegen.LocalVariable
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Assignable, Expression, Statement, TypedElement

    public class LocalVariable
extends java.lang.Object
implements Assignable, Expression
    A Java source code element that represents a local method variable. Represents a mutable reference which is both an Expression with a value and an Assignable reference.
